author: wn.com
title: US Has More Important Things to Do Than Blame Russia for MH17 Crash
text: Donald Trump, a leading Republican nominee for the 2016 presidential election, called on Americans to focus on making the US “great again,” rather than accusing Russia -- or anybody else, for that matter, without proof - of taking down the Malaysian airliner over the Donetsk region in the summer of 2014. ...
